# Interactions & Animations

## Transition Defaults

Apply to all interactive elements:

```css
a, button, [role="button"] {
  transition: 
    color 150ms ease-out,
    opacity 150ms ease-out,
    background-color 150ms ease-out,
    transform 150ms ease-out;
}
```

## Easing Functions

```css
:root {
  --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1);
  --ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  --ease-spring: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
}
```

## Link Hover Patterns

Underline reveals on hover with offset:

```css
a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--text-primary);
}

a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 2px;
  text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
}
```

Alternative - color change only:

```css
.subtle-link {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.subtle-link:hover {
  color: var(--text-primary);
}
```

## Opacity Hover

For images, icons, and cards:

```css
.card:hover {
  opacity: 0.6;
}

/* Or inverse - start muted, brighten on hover */
.icon {
  opacity: 0.5;
}

.icon:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}
```

## Button States

Include both hover AND pressed states:

```css
.button {
  background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
}

.button:hover {
  background-color: var(--bg-tertiary);
}

.button:active,
.button[data-pressed] {
  background-color: var(--border-primary);
  transform: scale(0.98);
}
```

## Arrow/Chevron Movement

Subtle translate on hover:

```css
.link-with-arrow:hover .arrow {
  transform: translateX(2px);
}

.arrow {
  transition: transform 150ms ease-out;
}
```

## Scrollbar Hiding

For cleaner scroll areas:

```css
.hide-scrollbar {
  scrollbar-width: none; /* Firefox */
  -ms-overflow-style: none; /* IE/Edge */
}

.hide-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none; /* Chrome/Safari */
}
```

## Focus Ring Pattern

Visible only on keyboard navigation:

```css
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

:focus:not(:focus-visible) {
  outline: none;
}
```

## Signature Interaction: Blur Focus Effect

When hovering one item, blur others (use sparingly):

```css
.interactive-list:hover .item:not(:hover) {
  opacity: 0.5;
  filter: blur(2px);
  transition: 
    opacity 250ms ease-out,
    filter 250ms ease-out;
}

.item {
  transition: 
    opacity 250ms ease-out,
    filter 250ms ease-out;
}
```

## Video Thumbnail Placeholder

Blur placeholder while video loads:

```css
.video-container {
  position: relative;
}

.placeholder {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  filter: blur(32px);
  transform: scale(1.2);
  z-index: 1;
}

.video {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}
```

## Animation Anti-Patterns

```css
/* ❌ Avoid */
transition: all 0.3s; /* Too vague, too slow */
animation: bounce 1s infinite; /* Distracting */
transform: scale(1.1); /* Too aggressive */

/* ✅ Prefer */
transition: opacity 150ms ease-out; /* Specific */
transform: translateX(2px); /* Subtle */
```

## Reduced Motion

Respect user preferences:

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

